<br>
Caveat: I have not quadded the Wyverns in CS, but the following is what I have been told, about would like to hear feedback on the following if you believe it to be true or not.<br>
<br>
[Minimum Level: 51]<br>
<br>
I am told this can be done at 44. Using CoF (about 16 of them) and 3 or so BoFs With KEI (a 10 minute kite will regen you around 800 mana) and a large mana pool (I have a 240 Int). It will take all of your mana, you may even have to run around for the KEI to replinish for the last CoF, but it is doable (I think). I will try this personally soon, but this the above is consistant with the advice of others who have.<br>
<br>
[Mob List (HP): Wyvern]<br>
<br>
They have about 3200 hps.<br>
<br>
[Availability (1-&gt;10): 2]<br>
<br>
Goes without saying I suppose, but probably depends on server. On the frequent trips to the Othmirs to turn in tusks, I've never seen any qudding going on Rodcet Nife.<br>
<br>
[Other Notes/Tips/Warnings: Often camped but very easy, Wyverns will not agro if you have a good faction with Claws of Veeshan, except for Yvolcarm and Azureake (the named Cobalt Drake).]<br>
<br>
I believe they are social though, so you can drag a agroed Wyvern through another to get agro even if you have good CoV faction.<br>
<br>
<br>
