<br>
There is also a Castle near the Dulak zone in that has tons of drogmar and shrooms to pull.  Its very wide open and is NEVER camped.  The only downside is the loot is non existant.  Though the Drogmar drop an item that has a single charge of Clarity.  But seriously who needs clarity with all the Kei for Donation going around. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lunaltoadsnatcher>Lunal Toadsnatcher</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 1351<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/6/03 5:55 pm)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Quad Kiting Locations Guide - Rough Draft</span><hr size=1> You do realize that a level 34 does not get the spell Atol's Spectral Shackles, right?   I assume you are talking about our other AOE snare spell. <br>
