<br>
Raptors are actually where you should be quadding for xp at 53 in TD.  Other than learning to break the large island spawns, its mindlessly boring, but great xp.  <br>
<br>
Hint for raptors:  make use of all of the limited space, especially for the initial breaks.  Round em up over the water (with levity on yourself) then run em in a straightline over to the beach.  <br>
<br>
-Tsu<br>
54 channeler  <br>
